A U.S. judge today dismissed lawsuit fired White House aide Lt. Col. Oliver North seeking halt special prosecutor 's investigation Iran arm scandal .
In 21-page ruling , U.S. District Court Judge Barrington Parker threw North 's suit challenging constitutionality law empowering special prosecutor Walsh investigate secret arm sale Iran diversion profit '' contra '' rebel Nicaragua .
`` The nation demand expeditious complete disclosure government 's involvement Iran-contra affair , '' Parker ruled .
